name: Jon Tope
text: In and out. Sweet can't beat the price

name: S L C
text: I love Little Caesars Pizza...but one thing I loved the best was their 'corn meal crust' and Whitefish does not have that... but I am trying to get over that for their friendly and pleasing service in Whitefish is the best I have ever …More

name: Cory Struth
text: Great staff!  Very helpful and kept 4 little boys happy:). Delicious hot pizza made quickly for an awesome price!!! Two thumbs up!!!

name: James Bowland
text: This location is closed, pour one out for good cheap pizza.

name: Rich Beeseet
text: Pizza was great, customer service was good, but had problems with online ordering at this store.  The order processed and was paid for but they did not receive order information at the store.  Basically had to re-order and wait for my pizza …More

name: Grant K
text: Best pizza in whitefish, totally better than 2nd Street and Jersey boys.

name: J Foster
text: Surprisingly good! Better than any other pizza we've had in Whitefish, and we've had them all.

name: Jeff Mironuck
text: Pretty bad pizza. Actually the worst I’ve ever had. Pretty disappointed. Sure doesn’t look like the pizza you see on tv.
